text: Alfredo Pelliccioni (born 21 June 1953) is a Sammarinese sports shooter. Pelliccioni competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics, the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics.Alfredo PelliccioniAlfredo PELLICCIONI == References == Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Sport shooters Category:Olympians for San Marino
